definition: An existence of an Organism (sensu http://rs.tdwg.org/dwc/terms/Organism) at a particular place at a particular time.
An action that occurs at some location during some time.
A spatial region or named place.
A taxonomic determination (e.g., the assignment to a taxon).
A group of organisms (sensu http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0100026) considered by taxonomists to form a homogeneous unit.
A specimen that has been preserved.
An interaction between two herbaria, e.g. loan or exchange.
A document or certificate giving permission to do something, e.g. collecting.
An image or other digital resource.
